In the treatment of aortic diseases, in addition to the treatment of dissecting aneurysms and aortic aneurysms, he has rich experience in emergency ruptured aortic aneurysms.
"The Department of Vascular Surgery, Zhongshan Hospital Affiliated to Xiamen University, is outstanding in this region in terms of the history of development, the breadth, difficulty, and complexity of the operation. Therefore, this time we established a collaboration center. In addition to the aorta, we can also In the diagnosis and treatment of lower extremity arteries, carotid arteries and other diseases, in-depth cooperation in all aspects of medicine, teaching and scientific research is carried out.
Professor Feng Rui, deputy director of the Department of Vascular Surgery of Shanghai Changhai Hospital, said.
